value.name: Entrance
value.text:
It is a very special day at the Zoo.  It is actually ${pages[10].characters[0].name} birthday today!
Visit each animal and they will give a unique gift for ${pages[10].characters[0].name}.

value.name: Apes
value.text: You head over to see the strong ${charactersByGroup(page,'monkeys')[0].name}.  They get their strength from eating a lot of fruits and ${page.items[0]}.  They offer some fruit salad with ${page.items[0]} to take to the party.  “Perfect!  But maybe keep the ${page.items[0]} on the side” you say.

value.name: Salmon Eaters
value.text: Next you see a ${charactersByGroup(page,'eat-salmon')[0].name}.  The ${charactersByGroup(page,'eat-salmon')[0].name} says “I just caught some delicious arctic salmon.  Could you bring this to ${pages[10].characters[0].name}’s party for me?  Mmmmm, salmon will make the guests very happy.

value.name: Singers
value.text:
Us ${page.characters[0].name}s have an acapella group.  We can sing Happy Birthday!
“I didn’t know ${page.characters[0].name}s could sing” you say.  “Sure we can” as they start singing Happy Birthday, you cover your ears and move on.

value.name: Fancy Animal
value.text: Every party needs some help to serve all of the refreshments.  The ${charactersByGroup(page,'fabulous')[0].name} are already dressed in their fancy attire and ready to serve some drinks.

value.name: Family need opener
value.text: “We need someone to open up our drinks…Does anyone have a bottle opener?”

value.name: Horned Animal
value.text: ${charactersByGroup(page,'with-horns')[0].name} can take care of that with his Horn!

value.name: Family Can Opener
value.text: “Wait.. but how will we open the caviar and pâtè?”

value.name: Teethed Animal
value.text: “I can take care of that with my razor sharp teeth” says ${charactersByGroup(page,'with-teeth')[0].name}.

value.name: Mokeys
value.text: You know monkeys are known for being party animals.  If they come and monkey around everyone will have a good time!

value.name: Birthday
value.text:
The party get’s underway at the Zoo. 
${page.characters[0].name} says “this is the best party in the history of the Zoo.  Let’s do this every year!”

value.name: Elephants
value.text: All elephants are great DJs and love to spin records with their trunks.  All the animals dance the night away.
